  "text": "We apply our method for the diagnosis of neurodegenerative brain disorders. Specifically, in this study, we use two popular databases: PPMI [CITATION_1] and ADNI [CITATION_2] . The former aims at investigating PD and its related disorders, while the latter is designed for diagnosing AD and its prodromal stage, known as Mild-Cognitive Impairment (MCI). In addition, to validate the proposed method, we further conduct experiments on synthetic data, as well as some benchmark datasets for semi-supervised learning.",
